@GetMapping("/orders")
public ResponseEntity<?> getOrders(
    @RequestParam(defaultValue = "1") int version) {

    if (version == 1) {
        // V1 response
    } else if (version == 2) {
        // V2 response
    }
}

// Usage: GET /api/orders?version=2
```

**Deprecation and migration:**

```java
// Mark old versions as deprecated
@Deprecated
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/api/v1/orders")
public class OrderControllerV1 {

    @PostMapping
    public ResponseEntity<OrderResponseV1> create(@RequestBody OrderRequestV1 req) {
        log.warn("Using deprecated API v1. Please migrate to /api/v2/");
